    Valve ranking of Counter-Strike Teams
    
Ranking follows Valve's model for ranking Counter-Strike teams.
                
    How is the ranking calculated?
    
The ranking takes into account the accomplishments of teams starting from the chosen date (in Copenhagen timezone), inclusive of that day and extending back over the previous six months.
